     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "NambuElements[mat, {a1, ..., an}] returns a list of linear combinations \
of the annihilation and creation operators of Dirac fermion modes {a1, ..., \
an} with the coefficients specified by the elements of matrix mat. \
NambuElements[mat, {c1, c2, ..., c 2 n}] returns a list of linear \
combinations of Majorana fermion operators {c1, c2, ..., c 2 n}, where the \
elements of complex matrix mat are the coefficients in the equivalent linear \
combinations of Dirac fermion operators (not the Majorana fermion operators \
themselves) corresponding to the Majorana fermion modes.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
